such beauty in my lifetime.

434
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:30,220
Those people mirror us completely.

435
00:27:33,359 --> 00:27:34,599
There's someone

436
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,599
who shares my fate

437
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:38,839
of being seen as cursed

438
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,160
and cast aside.

439
00:27:43,119 --> 00:27:44,279
(I'm too weak.)

440
00:27:44,279 --> 00:27:45,319
(I failed to protect you.)

441
00:27:46,116 --> 00:27:49,056
(The Immortal Lord said they'll select
a Sword Master to guard the seal.)

442
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,599
(I'll become the Sword Master for you.)

443
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,160
(I swear to protect you.)

444
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:58,119
(The Sword Master's duty
isn't merely safeguarding the seal.)

445
00:27:58,539 --> 00:27:59,339
(Your mission)

446
00:27:59,559 --> 00:28:02,460
(is to kill Bai Yixi,
who contains the Night Deity.)

447
00:28:02,759 --> 00:28:03,519
Chen,

448
00:28:03,759 --> 00:28:05,720
I don't want the Night Deity
to steal my body.

449
00:28:07,079 --> 00:28:07,880
I beg you.

450
00:28:08,839 --> 00:28:10,400
Please help me!

451
00:28:11,526 --> 00:28:14,424
♪Our fated bond clings unyielding♪

452
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,088
(If there's someone in this world
who's all for me,)

453
00:28:17,376 --> 00:28:18,279
(then my life journey)

454
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,400
(is never in vain.)

455
00:28:22,599 --> 00:28:23,880
(What wish did you make?)

456
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:27,400
(May Bai Yixi find peace and happiness.)

457
00:28:29,612 --> 00:28:35,490
